#: src/security.md:1
msgid "Security"
msgstr ""

#: src/security.md:3
msgid ""
"`rustup` is secure enough for most people, but it [still needs work](https://"
"github.com/rust-lang/rustup/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3Asecurity). "
"`rustup` performs all downloads over HTTPS, but does not yet validate "
"signatures of downloads."
msgstr ""

#: src/security.md:9
msgid ""
"File modes on installation honor umask as of 1.18.4, use umask if very tight "
"controls are desired."
msgstr ""

#: src/security.md:12
msgid ""
"If you wish to report a security issue, please follow the [Rust security "
"policy](https://www.rust-lang.org/policies/security)."
msgstr ""
